The '''Naval Command''',<ref name="Testimony">{{WEGCite|story=Admiral Jerjerrod's Testimony|book=Imperial Sourcebook}}</ref> also known as '''GAR Fleet Command''', was the command hierarchy of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Navy]] under the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].<ref name="Siege">''[[Clone Wars Gambit: Siege]]''</ref> [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Jerjerrod (admiral)|Jerjerrod]] served on it.<ref name="Testimony" /> Naval command would become [[Naval Command (Imperial)|Imperial Star Fleet Command]] under the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="The Constancia Affair">"[[The Constancia Affair]]"</ref> 

